+-----------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${PKGSTEM} on OpenBSD
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------

By default, koboredux contains only low-resolution graphics and sound.
To play the game in higher quality, purchase the full game from
https://olofson.itch.io/kobo-redux and copy the sfx/redux/, gfx/redux/,
and gfx/redux_fullscreen/ directories to ${TRUEPREFIX}/share/koboredux/.
